Usage: report_bundled_bus [-help] [-name <string>] [-nets <string>]
                          [-type {user_defined tool_inferred}] [-unmerged] [ [ > | >> ] ]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-name <string>                         # Name of the user defined bus group(s)
                                       # to be reported (list, optional)
-nets <string>                         # Name of net(s) to be reported
                                       # (list, optional)
-type {user_defined tool_inferred}     # Reports type of bundled bus to be
                                       # reported. (enum, optional)
-unmerged                              # Generate report without bus merging
                                       # (bool, optional)
> <filename>                           # Redirect output to file
                                       # (redirect_operator, optional)
>> <filename>                          # Append to output file
                                       # (redirect_operator, optional)